{"word":"Molech","slug":"molech","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Molech</b> <a href=\"#/H4432\">H4432</a> <br/> Called also Moloch and Milcom.<br/> An idol of the Ammonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=43'>Act 7:43</a><br/> Worshiped by the wives of Solomon, and by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=8'>1Ki 11:8</a><br/> Children sacrificed to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=35'>Jer 32:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=3'>2Ki 16:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=6'>2Ki 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=3'>2Ch 28:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=57&verse=5'>Isa 57:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=31'>Jer 7:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=21'>Eze 16:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=20&verse=26'>Eze 20:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=20&verse=31'>Eze 20:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=23&verse=37'>Eze 23:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=23&verse=39'>Eze 23:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=21'>Lev 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=5'>Lev 20:5</a>"}]}